<ul>
  <li>Implementation of Game of life ( http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Conway%27s_Game_of_Life ) with some extensions:</li>
  <li>
   <ul>
     <li>State for a cell can be one of [RED, GREEN, BLUE, DEAD] instead of only [ALIVE, DEAD]</li>
     <li>Any cell can change its state not according with GoL rules with a given (very low) probability</li>
     <li>A cell, born according with GoF rules, must have the color state that is most present in the neighbourhood</li>
   </ul>
  </li>
</ul>
<ul>
  <li>Requirements:</li>
  <li>
     <ul>
       <li>Ruby</li>
       <li>Chingu gem and its requirements (gem install chingu)</li>
     </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

